column7: This Ball Point Stainless Steel Set Screw was described on the drawing as McMaster-Carr p/n 92605A113 Flat Point Stainless Steel Set Screw. This did not agree with the actual part purchased.  Removed McMaster-Carr part number from the drawing and changed  Flat Point to a Ball Point in the specification on the drawing. Changed M4 Thread Length from 8mm to 5mm as per actual part purchased. Shown a 2mm Hex Key hole in one end of the Screw.  This part is being manufactured by vendor to our drawing specification.
